hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I like watching TV www.arkopharma.com.tr On another occasion, I boarded a flight from Chicago to Los Angeles and I told the flight attendant that I was allergic to nuts and asked that they didn’t serve them on the flight. She then told me that she would have get security to take me off the plane. It was awful. I told her that I had a life-threatening allergy and that I carry an EpiPen. She said I would have to give up my first-class ticket and sit in the back of the plane where they wouldn’t be serving peanuts if I wanted to remain on the flight, so I gave up my first-class ticket and went and sat in economy.
